&quot;It&#39;s the same almost every day,&quot; said Huang Jing, 20, who studies sales in her spare time.
&quot;All routine.&quot;
One reason is that the female officers are not allowed to confiscate the traders&#39; goods like their male colleagues.
They can only threaten offenders with reporting them to their male superiors.
