The final strategy of Juan Carlos, Pablo, Emilio, Marta y Elvira Álvarez Mezquiriz is interpreted by David Álvarez as a &quot;desperate means by the claimants - his five children - to use legal sophistry, fraud and abuse of rights to impose the annulled March 18 Assembly . January to be recognized&quot;, as official spokesmen explain.
