On the other hand, he pointed out that in China, state authorities have worked together with central and local governments to achieve the goals of energy saving, energy efficient use and emissions reduction.
He also said several multi-year plans have already been launched or completed, both those funded by the Chinese government and those receiving funds from other countries.
